('researcher-1', 'Dr. Rajesh Kumar', 'IIT Delhi', 'Professor of Computer Science', NULL, 'Leading researcher in Natural Language Processing and Computer Vision with 15+ years of experience. Pioneer in developing transformer models for Indian languages.', ARRAY['Natural Language Processing', 'Computer Vision', 'Deep Learning', 'Multilingual AI'], ARRAY['Transformer Models for Indian Languages (2024)', 'Vision Systems for Agricultural AI (2023)', 'Low-Resource Language Processing (2022)'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/rajeshkumar', 'https://scholar.google.com/rajeshkumar', 5000, 45, 0, true, NOW(), NOW()),
